<TITLE>Sound Stage - The History of Motion Picture Sound</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY ALINK="BEIGE" BACKGROUND="redgradientvertical.jpg"  LEFTMARGIN="20" LINK="#FFEF9F" text="gold" vlink ="tan" bgcolor="#672929"><BASEFONT SIZE="3">
